  D --> E["4. Submit + Tanda Tangan Akad"]:::p
  E --> F{"Ada pinjaman<br/>aktif?"}:::d
  F -->|Ya| R1["Tolak — HTTP 409"]:::no
  F -->|Tidak| G{"Decision Engine"}:::d
  G -->|Reject| R2["REJECTED + notifikasi"]:::no
  G -->|Refer| H["Review Analyst → Approver"]:::p
  H --> G
  G -->|Approve| I["5. Pencairan (disbursement)<br/>+ generate jadwal cicilan"]:::ok
  I --> J["6. Repayment berjalan"]:::p
  J --> K{"Pembayaran"}:::d
  K -->|Penuh & tepat| J
  K -->|Sebagian| L["PARTIALLY_PAID<br/>sisa jadi tunggakan"]:::d
  K -->|Telat| M["OVERDUE + denda<br/>DPD naik → Kol 2..5"]:::no
  L --> J
  M --> N{"Direstrukturisasi?"}:::d
